Yet Another Rogue-Like

a placeholder name for a placeholder game

using the glorious libtcod 1.5.0

code is commented in a moon language

author is not responsible for aneurysms caused by peeking into the code
please compile under medical supervision with your eyes firmly closed

hacked together haphazardly by The Martin

keys:
arrows for movement
D for drop
G for grab
I for inventory
alt-enter to toggle fullscreen